 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Recommends: libgl1-pvr-dri
Description: X.Org X server -- pvr display driver
 This driver for the X.Org X server (see xserver-xorg for a further
 description) provides support for PowerVR cards.

